_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999949341145, \"rank\": 5.065984732868899e-09, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8405266867429508, \"rank\": 0.18948520912653047, \"text\": \"Winter Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997821065229444, \"rank\": 0.00021634912262323078, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 400, \"end\": 404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9973327826237784, \"rank\": 0.0026743504098556007, \"text\": \"U.N.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999993760142971, \"rank\": 3.2910312817741287e-07, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9995532028094253, \"rank\": 0.0004469966802276606, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC leader, whosefinal termas president ends next year, praised the U.N. General Assembly's support for the \\\"Pact for the Future\\\"that contained several references to sport, including a commitment to \\\"invest in accessible, safe, inclusive and equitable quality education for all, including physical education and sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 624, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.603601526389823e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9973327826237784, \"rank\": 0.0026743504098556007, \"text\": \"U.N.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 697, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_General_Assembly\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.345726712161784e-12, \"text\": \"General Assembly\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_General_Assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_General_Assembly\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bach focused on peace as the \\\"most fundamental\\\" goal, saying the IOC was proud of being able to bring together athletes from 206 countries with national Olympic committees as well as the largest-ever refugee team to compete in Paris.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999949341145, \"rank\": 5.065984732868899e-09, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.603601526389823e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997633283608, \"rank\": 2.3667160354436275e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes from Russia and Belarus, however, had to compete under aneutral statusdue to the ongoing attack against Ukraine.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9985960322726151, \"rank\": 0.001394032592217229, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9992562928236879, \"rank\": 0.0007442316932399569, \"text\": \"Belarus\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}, {\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9998051669223534, \"rank\": 0.00017659005784928533, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite fierce competition during the Summer Games, Bach said the athlete